# Faz 0: Monorepo Scaffold

## Goal

pnpm workspaces + Turborepo ile monorepo iskeleti kurulur: `apps/{api,web,worker}`, `packages/{shared,dto,policy}`, paylaşımlı ESLint/Prettier/TypeScript config, Husky + commitlint + lint-staged, minimal CI pipeline. NestJS/React implementasyonu yok — yalnızca placeholder entrypoint'ler. Faz sonunda `pnpm install`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck` green. Altyapı cloud-only: RDS + S3 + KMS + ClamAV (ECS) AWS üzerinden; local Docker Compose yok.

Detay: `Docs/10_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md` §Faz 0.

